<verse number="3" style="v" />My whole body is sick because of your anger;</para>

<para style="q1">there is no health in my bones because of my sin.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />For my iniquities overwhelm me;</para>

<para style="q1">they are a burden too heavy for me.</para>
